BitcoinTalk Translation Bounty  Bitcointalk Translation Bounty Campaign : 300,000 RoleCoin to be distributed on first come first serve basis  *IMPORTANT UPDATE REGARDING TRANSLATION BOUNTY* How to  participate in "TRANSLATION BOUNTY"  *PROCEDURE* Translate ANN and White paper of "RoleCoin"into any languages,and post them on respective language Boards and then share the link with us Then fill up the application form Please do not share the link of your previous work on spread sheet   Rewards:  Jr.Member:20 RoleCoin per post Member: 40 RoleCoin per post Full Member: 80 RoleCoinper post Senior Member: 160 RoleCoin per post Hero Member: 300 RoleCoin per post Legendary: 500 RoleCoin per post  You will receive 200 additional RoleCoin every week for wearing the rolecoin avatar and Signature Codes.
